imdb.plot outline: Hosted by Carrie Keagan for it's first nine seasons then Nick Lachey for it's final season, Big Morning Buzz Live is a fun and edgy, one-hour morning talk show on VH1 that provides a live, daily dose of pop culture news, chat, music and entertainment. Presented live from the lobby of VH1's headquarters in New York City, the show offers up-to-the-minute topical headlines, engaging celebrity interviews, live musical performances and in-depth conversations with insiders, bloggers and experts in a variety of fields from Music, Movies, TV and everything in between.
